run(sql="
with cte as(
    select a.orderDate, a.subOrderId, b.pogId 
    from `temp.final_attri2` a left join `all(agCmDump)` b 
    on a.subOrderId=b.subOrderId 
    where a.Channel LIKE 'FB%' and a.orderDate = '2023-03-01' or a.orderDate = '2023-03-02'
),

cte2 as(
    select cte.orderDate, cte.pogId, count(distinct cte.subOrderId) as orders, sum(b.nm) as total_nm 
    from cte  
    left join `all(unitEconomicsBaseTable)` b 
    on cte.subOrderId=b.subOrderId
    group by cte.orderDate, cte.pogId
)


select cte2.orderDate, cte2.pogId, cte2.orders, cte2.total_nm/cte2.orders as NMSO, b.NMSO as predicted_NMSO
from cte2 
left join `temp.pnm1` b 
on cte2.pogId=b.pogId   
    
",1000)
